WEBVTT

00:02.602 --> 00:03.635
[ Remote clicks ]

00:03.670 --> 00:05.204
[ Upbeat music plays ]

00:07.741 --> 00:10.609
♪ I don't care what you say! ♪

00:11.945 --> 00:13.912
♪ I'm gonna do what I want
all day! ♪

00:13.947 --> 00:16.548
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:16.583 --> 00:18.483
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:18.518 --> 00:22.921
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:25.292 --> 00:29.327
[ Dramatic music plays ]

00:29.362 --> 00:33.598
Vroom! Pew!
[ Laughs ] Take that!

00:33.633 --> 00:35.333
Okay, Mayor,
time to focus.

00:35.368 --> 00:38.336
We only have a few more things
to sign, and then you can play.

00:38.371 --> 00:40.939
[ Grumbles ]
Just a few more?

00:40.974 --> 00:43.075
Last ones.

00:43.110 --> 00:45.343
[ Mumbling ] Mayor --
telling me not to play.

00:45.378 --> 00:49.381
What's this? - This is the new
redistricting initiative from Lofton.

00:49.416 --> 00:55.854
Uh. Uh -- Um --
Eh -- good enough.

00:55.889 --> 00:57.055
[ Laughs ]

00:57.090 --> 00:59.524
♪♪

00:59.559 --> 01:03.395
Sumo! Oh, Sumo!
Time for school!

01:03.430 --> 01:04.796
[ Dog barking ]

01:04.831 --> 01:07.866
Hold your horses!
We're gonna be late!

01:07.901 --> 01:10.202
[ Grunts ]

01:10.237 --> 01:11.804
Oh!

01:13.573 --> 01:15.607
Morning, sleepy head.

01:15.642 --> 01:17.442
[ Dogs bark ]

01:17.477 --> 01:20.746
[ Giggling ]

01:23.250 --> 01:25.750
[ Laughter ]

01:25.785 --> 01:27.152
[ School bell rings ]

01:27.187 --> 01:30.655
Okay, has anyone seen Camden
this morning?

01:30.690 --> 01:33.325
I'm right here,
Miss Baker.

01:33.360 --> 01:35.494
Sumo:
Sardine, madame?

01:35.529 --> 01:37.562
Clarence:
Oh don't mind if I do!

01:37.597 --> 01:39.731
A garden salad for you,
sir?

01:39.766 --> 01:41.833
Oh, no thank you.
Just this will do.

01:41.868 --> 01:44.102
[ Gulping ]
- [ Laughs ]

01:44.137 --> 01:46.905
We can make a tunnel
to the cafeteria

01:46.940 --> 01:50.308
and be first in line for pizza day!
- Yeah!

01:50.343 --> 01:53.445
Look!
I'm expecting!

01:53.480 --> 01:54.813
Expecting what?

01:54.848 --> 01:56.414
[ Clunk ]

01:56.449 --> 01:57.983
Both: Whoa.

01:58.018 --> 01:59.918
Lofton --
every year they redistrict

01:59.953 --> 02:02.187
just so they can take
more of our kids!

02:02.222 --> 02:03.655
Oh, gosh.
It's looking like

02:03.690 --> 02:05.590
we're losing
quite a few this time.

02:05.625 --> 02:07.359
Let's see.
We're losing Dunkin Bambi.

02:07.394 --> 02:09.861
And Regis Gilben. Mr. Reese:
Like the son I never had.

02:09.896 --> 02:12.531
Oh, wow. We're also
losing Sumo this year.

02:12.566 --> 02:13.999
Sumowski!

02:14.034 --> 02:16.201
[ Munching ]
Ol' peanut head's

02:16.236 --> 02:18.670
gonna be - someone else's problem now.
[ Metal clanking ]

02:18.705 --> 02:22.941
[ Grunting ]

02:22.976 --> 02:25.677
[ Muffled ] Hey! Sumowksi!
What?

02:25.712 --> 02:27.546
Pack it up, son.
You're switching schools!

02:27.581 --> 02:30.549
What?
- You're switching schools!

02:30.584 --> 02:32.350
Maybe
we're in trouble.

02:32.385 --> 02:34.052
You're not in trouble!

02:34.087 --> 02:38.490
I said moving schools!

02:38.525 --> 02:40.492
Whaaaa?

02:40.527 --> 02:43.728
[ Grunting ]
Now you're in trouble!

02:43.763 --> 02:45.897
Looks like they changed
the school-zone border,

02:45.932 --> 02:47.666
so now Sumo's
got to change schools?

02:47.701 --> 02:49.734
Yep.
- I wonder how they decided.

02:49.769 --> 02:52.003
Seems pretty arbitrary.
Yep.

02:52.038 --> 02:54.005
I guess it's the way
things have to be.

02:54.040 --> 02:56.474
Yep. There's a lot more stuff
here than I thought.

02:56.509 --> 02:58.076
Okay.
This is it then.

02:58.111 --> 03:00.145
No! No!

03:00.180 --> 03:01.546
No!

03:01.581 --> 03:03.248
No!
- Hey, man, what gives!

03:03.283 --> 03:06.651
I don't want you to go!
Well, I don't want to!

03:06.686 --> 03:08.019
I got to go
to a whole new school

03:08.054 --> 03:09.588
with a bunch
of weirdo new kids --

03:09.623 --> 03:12.224
Don't you worry, Sumo.
You're gonna stay right here.

03:12.259 --> 03:15.827
Muwah. - Uh, I don't think
- West Aberdale's that far.

03:15.862 --> 03:17.729
Hey, you shut your mouth,
Jeff.

03:17.764 --> 03:19.764
I will not!

03:19.799 --> 03:22.701
Listen, West Aberdale
has a really good curriculum.

03:22.736 --> 03:25.137
This could be a fresh start
for Sumo.

03:26.439 --> 03:28.106
No, Sumo, you're staying.

03:28.141 --> 03:30.008
Yeah? Yeah!

03:30.043 --> 03:32.444
Let's go tell those boobies
"no way"!

03:32.479 --> 03:34.613
Yeah!
- Aw, man.

03:34.648 --> 03:36.581
[ Beeping ]

03:36.616 --> 03:38.950
[ Laughter ]

03:38.985 --> 03:41.786
Sumo can't leave!
Yeah, no way!

03:41.821 --> 03:43.955
Both: [ Chanting ] No go Sumo.
No go Sumo. No go Sumo!

03:43.990 --> 03:46.791
You boys are in a lot of trouble
barging in here!

03:46.826 --> 03:49.728
Children in the teacher's
lounge, is that legal?

03:49.763 --> 03:52.464
Okay, okay, Clarence!
What's this all about?!

03:52.499 --> 03:54.199
You're kicking out
Sumo!

03:54.234 --> 03:55.734
You can't just treat him
differently

03:55.769 --> 03:57.269
just 'cause he looks weird.
- Hey!

03:57.304 --> 04:00.472
Or lives somewhere else. And send him far!
- Yeah!

04:00.507 --> 04:02.874
It's not even that far.
Yeah, right!

04:02.909 --> 04:05.243
It might
as well be California!

04:05.278 --> 04:07.145
Don't put me on a boat!

04:07.180 --> 04:10.382
We'll be so old the next time
we see each other, Sumo.

04:10.417 --> 04:14.319
Well, here's what I think
of West Aberdale!

04:14.354 --> 04:18.490
[ Farting noise ]

04:18.525 --> 04:21.193
Okay. Okay, hold --

04:23.029 --> 04:25.797
[ Panting ]

04:25.832 --> 04:28.667
Listen, guys, this is hard --
I know.

04:28.702 --> 04:30.268
But it's completely
out of our control.

04:30.303 --> 04:31.670
Sumo's not the only one.

04:31.705 --> 04:35.073
This affects<i> all</i> kids who live
west of Eschelmen Drive.

04:35.108 --> 04:38.276
Kids who live on this side stay
at our Aberdale Elementary.

04:38.311 --> 04:41.079
And kids over here
move to West Aberdale.

04:41.114 --> 04:44.516
Unfortunately,
Sumo's house is here.

04:44.551 --> 04:47.052
Sorry, guys.
It's out of our hands.

04:48.688 --> 04:51.423
That's it?
- There's nothing we can do?

04:51.458 --> 04:52.490
I don't know, man.

04:52.525 --> 04:54.426
I can't just
live somewhere else.

04:54.461 --> 04:57.195
[ Gasps ]
Or can you?

04:57.230 --> 04:58.196
What?

04:58.231 --> 05:00.632
See you...later.

05:00.667 --> 05:02.867
Later?
- But we ain't playing later.

05:02.902 --> 05:05.637
Or are we?
- I don't think so?

05:05.672 --> 05:07.806
Or are you?

05:07.841 --> 05:11.543
Okay, I'm leaving.
Or are you?

05:11.578 --> 05:13.778
Clarence,
where are we going?

05:13.813 --> 05:15.547
Someplace safe.

05:15.582 --> 05:18.550
Sumo...
Welcome to your new home!

05:18.585 --> 05:21.720
[ Chickens clucking ]

05:21.755 --> 05:23.988
[ Pecking ]

05:24.023 --> 05:28.460
[ Laughs ] This is awesome!
It's my own place!

05:28.495 --> 05:30.962
Well,
plus the chickens.

05:30.997 --> 05:33.631
And we'll still get to go
to school together.

05:33.666 --> 05:36.000
I'm so happy right now!

05:36.035 --> 05:38.303
I feel pretty good,
too, man.

05:38.338 --> 05:42.574
[ Clucking ]

05:42.609 --> 05:45.077
Well, good night, Sumo!

05:50.283 --> 05:52.350
[ Clucking continues ]

05:52.385 --> 05:55.153
Oh, man.

05:55.188 --> 05:58.590
[ Grunting ]

05:58.625 --> 05:59.924
[ Clucking stops ]

05:59.959 --> 06:01.826
[ Clucking resumes ]

06:01.861 --> 06:02.827
[ Grunts ]

06:02.862 --> 06:03.828
[ Clucking stops ]

06:03.863 --> 06:06.664
[ Clucking resumes ]

06:06.699 --> 06:08.733
[ Clarence snores ]

06:08.768 --> 06:13.438
Mmm...
What a wonderful pie!

06:13.473 --> 06:15.607
Hey, Clarence.

06:15.642 --> 06:18.777
[ Yawns ]
Sumo, is that you?

06:18.812 --> 06:21.679
Could you close the window?
It's freezing.

06:21.714 --> 06:25.016
I can't sleep in that coop.
Can I crash with you?

06:25.051 --> 06:29.421
Oh, well,
- Mr. Frogs got the top bunk.

06:29.456 --> 06:31.122
[ Frog croaks ]

06:31.157 --> 06:34.726
Anyway, he gets pretty cranky
if you wake him up.

06:34.761 --> 06:36.561
Oh, okay.

06:36.596 --> 06:41.299
But, hey, if you want to come
sleep with me that's cool.

06:41.334 --> 06:42.367
Eh...

06:42.402 --> 06:44.269
[ Clarence snores ]

06:44.304 --> 06:47.005
I think
I'm just gonna go, man.

06:48.508 --> 06:52.777
Sumo! Oh, Sumo!
I made you breakfast.

06:52.812 --> 06:56.147
[ Gasps ]
[ Dramatic music ]

06:56.182 --> 06:59.150
S-Sumo?
Where are you?!

06:59.185 --> 07:00.585
Sumo?!

07:00.620 --> 07:02.987
Those teachers
must've took him!

07:03.022 --> 07:06.057
I'm coming for you, Sumo!

07:06.092 --> 07:09.427
Wow.
- You're a little gentleman!

07:09.462 --> 07:10.728
I look weird.

07:10.763 --> 07:13.398
No...
No. No. No!

07:13.433 --> 07:17.302
What are you doing?
That's a West Aberdale uniform!

07:17.337 --> 07:21.406
If you love it so much
[Grunts] take it.

07:21.441 --> 07:25.343
Oh, my.
- Maybe I'll just try it on.

07:25.378 --> 07:26.511
Wow.

07:26.546 --> 07:27.846
What? What's that?

07:27.881 --> 07:30.748
That's correct.
- I do go to West Aberdale.

07:30.783 --> 07:32.684
Thanks for noticing!
[ Door opens ]

07:32.719 --> 07:36.821
Jeffrey?
They -- they got you too?

07:36.856 --> 07:39.524
I-I was just
trying on Sumo's uniform.

07:39.559 --> 07:42.126
Okay, that's good.
- Because now you can take it off.

07:42.161 --> 07:43.695
What?
Clarence, calm down!

07:43.730 --> 07:47.032
How can I be calm when everyone
keeps taking my friends away?

07:48.368 --> 07:50.635
Aah!
- Clarence, what the heck?

07:50.670 --> 07:52.470
You ruined it.

07:52.505 --> 07:55.840
Fine. If you guys are so in love
with West Aberdale,

07:55.875 --> 07:58.142
I guess I'm all alone.

07:58.177 --> 08:01.813
[ Sighs ]
I'll go get him.

08:01.848 --> 08:04.716
[ Sobbing ]

08:04.751 --> 08:07.185
Okay, think, Clarence, think. [
Woman yelling indistinctly ]

08:07.220 --> 08:10.321
How can you save your friends?
There's got to be a way.

08:10.356 --> 08:11.222
Wait a second...

08:11.257 --> 08:13.024
Street signs.
Of course!

08:13.059 --> 08:15.059
If I get rid of
all the street signs,

08:15.094 --> 08:16.461
no one will know
where they live!

08:16.496 --> 08:17.562
It's genius!

08:17.597 --> 08:19.864
But how do I
get rid of the street signs?

08:19.899 --> 08:22.333
Bingo!

08:22.368 --> 08:23.801
Aah!

08:23.836 --> 08:26.337
I'll make a new world
with no borders!

08:26.372 --> 08:31.142
And the only place to live
is with me!

08:31.177 --> 08:34.579
Oh yeah, enjoying this nice
West Aberdale weather?

08:34.614 --> 08:36.681
[ Giggles ] I know I am.

08:36.716 --> 08:39.250
Ahhhh!
It's out of control!

08:39.285 --> 08:41.553
Clarence,
what are you doing?

08:41.588 --> 08:43.254
I'm destroying everything!

08:43.289 --> 08:45.023
Get down.
You're gonna get hurt!

08:45.058 --> 08:46.691
I'm already hurt, Sumo.

08:46.726 --> 08:48.760
I can't go to school
without you.

08:48.795 --> 08:53.031
Look, man, it's gonna be weird,
but maybe it could be cool.

08:53.066 --> 08:56.935
Like it'd be cool if you could
stop trying to stop it

08:56.970 --> 08:59.437
and see
if it might be cool!

08:59.472 --> 09:01.706
It might be cool...

09:01.741 --> 09:04.442
It might be cool?

09:04.477 --> 09:06.911
Sumo,
I-I want to get down...

09:06.946 --> 09:08.580
Jump, Clarence! Jump!

09:08.615 --> 09:09.914
[ Grunting ]

09:09.949 --> 09:11.316
[ Smash ]

09:13.486 --> 09:15.386
So it might be cool?

09:15.421 --> 09:16.922
Mm.

09:19.092 --> 09:22.860
Sumo! You're gonna be late
for your new school!

09:22.895 --> 09:25.697
[ Panting ]

09:25.732 --> 09:30.568
♪ I'll be there no matter when
just hold on to me and then ♪

09:30.603 --> 09:34.238
♪ We can ride together
and I just hope ♪

09:34.273 --> 09:37.308
♪ That
we'll always be friends ♪

09:37.343 --> 09:42.380
[ School bell rings ] ♪ I just hope
that we'll always be friends ♪

09:42.415 --> 09:46.150
Class, I'd like to welcome
our new students today.

09:46.185 --> 09:49.921
Ryan, why don't you
introduce yourself?

09:49.956 --> 09:53.791
Hi. My name is Sumo.

09:53.826 --> 09:56.127
Goodbye, sweet prince.

09:56.162 --> 09:58.429
♪ Things are fine now
you're not here ♪

09:58.464 --> 10:01.499
♪ I'm still smiling
full of cheer ♪

10:01.534 --> 10:03.601
♪ I'll reach out
to others near ♪

10:03.636 --> 10:06.571
♪ They're not the same
but it's okay ♪

10:06.606 --> 10:11.342
♪ I joke and hope it might be
the kind of thing you'd like ♪

10:11.377 --> 10:14.345
♪ If it's not
then that's all right ♪

10:14.380 --> 10:19.150
♪ I just hope
that we'll always be friends ♪

10:19.185 --> 10:22.954
♪ I just hope
that we'll always be friends ♪

10:22.989 --> 10:25.423
[ Sighs ]

10:25.458 --> 10:28.526
Sumo?
What are you doing here?

10:28.561 --> 10:31.496
I don't know.
- I just wanted to hang out.

10:31.531 --> 10:35.299
But we go to different schools
now.

10:35.334 --> 10:37.869
We can still hang out
after school.

10:37.904 --> 10:39.037
[ Boing! ]

10:39.072 --> 10:40.338
I did not think
about that.

10:40.373 --> 10:44.008
[ Chuckles ]
What do you want to do?

10:44.043 --> 10:46.511
Hmm...

10:46.546 --> 10:48.046
Clarence:
[ Laughs ] Okay,

10:48.081 --> 10:50.448
maybe we can connect
our tunnels at Rough Riders!

10:50.483 --> 10:51.549
Copy that.

10:51.584 --> 10:55.453
Okay!
- And then lets dig to the ocean.

10:55.488 --> 10:58.356
Yeah! Oh! But I call dibs
on any pirate treasure.

10:58.391 --> 11:01.559
Well, then I call dibs
on any chicken nuggets.

11:01.594 --> 11:03.561
Roger that.

11:05.097 --> 11:06.864
♪ Early to bed ♪

11:08.434 --> 11:10.535
♪ Early to rise ♪

11:12.071 --> 11:15.440
♪ Picking my nose ♪
